* {{a|GenAm}} {{IPA|/ɡæfɚ/|lang=en}}
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/ɡæfə/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|æfə(ɹ)|lang=en}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|film}} A [[chief]] [[lighting]] [[technician]] for a motion-picture or television production.
# A [[glassblower]].
